{"tid":1694020,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"政府又黎！唔理科大生，慰問新華社！","createTime":"2019-11-05T02:24:54.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-06T06:13:10.000Z","uid":74778,"like":12,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"ce7c367e524995b017ad6d3ca45ced5dfb290372","tid":1694020,"uid":74778,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-05T02:24:54.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">張建宗到訪新華社亞太總分社表達慰問</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n位於灣仔的新華社亞太總分社辦公樓上周六被示威者破壞，署理行政長官張建宗昨天上午到訪大樓表達慰問。<br />\n<br />\n新華社報道，張建宗察看大堂受損情況，並<span style=\"color: red;\">慰問辦公樓內工作的新華社編採人員。張建宗表示，暴徒打砸破壞新華社亞太總分社辦公樓的行徑已經超越法治、文明和自由的底線，傷害全國人民的感情，令人無法接受，特區政府予以強烈譴責。</span><br />\n<br />\n他指出，事件再次表明，止暴制亂是香港眼下當務之急。特區政府已動員各部門，上下一心，全力以赴止暴制亂，希望讓香港盡快恢復穩定。<br />\n<br />\n張建宗同時說，特區政府已展開與社會各界的對話，並<span style=\"color: red;\">著手解決社會深層次矛盾</span>，希望轉危為機，讓香港盡早走出困局。他又說，在國家支持和各方共同努力下，香港有信心、有能力克服眼下困難，挺過難關。<br />\n<br />\n<em><a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1490089-20191105.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1490089-20191105.htm&d=kDaEa4B9Gv5qH72Sa3%2FdwONdVtVfIexd6qH9K0u6Sk4%3D&h=4dcd6402\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1490089-20191105.htm&h=81e58e8d\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1490089-20191105.htm</a></em><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">每次政府提深層次矛盾，我就諗到佢完全唔想解決呢d矛盾<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n上次唔理721 831 101，淨係去清真寺，有無搞撚錯啊！</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0RgMfXg.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0RgMfXg.jpg&h=19f59dc2&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Gu8yFpb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FGu8yFpb.jpg&h=b0921906&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/GWTuYa9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FGWTuYa9.jpg&h=21a03731&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"141713090353d11eba08e695c5e4fffa5f0605a2","tid":1694020,"uid":14897,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-05T02:30:15.000Z","msg":"死物。。。。。。"},{"pid":"a5dfebaa5d5b5b5684c3057136b76507f1002873","tid":1694020,"uid":214192,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-05T02:33:55.000Z","msg":"政府：香港人條命連啲死物都不如"},{"pid":"baea6f5750ebc1cf853d8f1d4afccdaf4af1d18a","tid":1694020,"uid":74778,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"quote":{"pid":"141713090353d11eba08e695c5e4fffa5f0605a2","tid":1694020,"uid":14897,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-05T02:30:15.000Z","msg":"死物。。。。。。"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-05T02:35:48.000Z","msg":"林鄭月娥政府不關心以下哪項...<br />\n<br />\nA. 黨鐵閘機<br />\nB. 清真寺大閘<br />\nC. 新華社玻璃<br />\nD. 香港人性命"},{"pid":"2d905978e8d3aba63931525194d7b50ed40f2046","tid":1694020,"uid":14897,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"baea6f5750ebc1cf853d8f1d4afccdaf4af1d18a","tid":1694020,"uid":74778,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"quote":{"pid":"141713090353d11eba08e695c5e4fffa5f0605a2","tid":1694020,"uid":14897,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-05T02:30:15.000Z","msg":"死物。。。。。。"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-05T02:35:48.000Z","msg":"林鄭月娥政府不關心以下哪項...<br />\n<br />\nA. 黨鐵閘機<br />\nB. 清真寺大閘<br />\nC. 新華社玻璃<br />\nD. 香港人性命"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-05T02:36:16.000Z","msg":"D<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fb788cc6b0238f1ed60ac2d699c830fcb333e331","tid":1694020,"uid":83910,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-05T02:36:27.000Z","